The paper deals with the security and privacy of face representations, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and computer vision (cs.CV). The use of fully homomorphic encryption (FHE) suggests a focus on cryptography (cs.CR) and the dimensionality reduction scheme may involve machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM). The potential privacy concerns may also relate to cybernetics (cs.CY).
